The paper discusses the secure exchange of information over wireless networks, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the physical properties of the wireless medium, which could fall under the category of signal processing (cs.SI) or multimedia (cs.MM).
